In summary, we consider all these morphologies to belong to a single polymorphic species, A. dybowskii , rendering A. andrusovi , A. brusinai and A. marina its junior subjective synonyms. This also makes the subgenus Horatia ( Caspiohydrobia ) Logvinenko & Starobogatov, 1969 , with H. marina as type species, a junior subjective synonym of Andrusovia (see also
Anistratenko et al . 2019
).
